title: Part A
stimulusHtml:
1 point is earned for zero slope at each point (x, y) where x = 0 or y = 1

1 point is earned for positive slope at each point (x, y) where x ≠ 0 or y > 1 and for negative slope at each point (x, y) where x ≠ 0 or y < 1
